title: Perfect day for Hiram House Camp pumpkin festival
text:
Perfect day for Hiram House Camp pumpkin festival 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
The 44th annual Hiram House pumpkin festival had perfect fall weather and a huge turnout. Proceeds will provide 'camperships' for youngsters...
